95
00:18:09,839 --> 00:18:09,920
[SPEAKER_02] godine.

96
00:18:10,559 --> 00:18:12,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ja nazovem jednog prijatelja, neću sad njegovo ime.

97
00:18:14,559 --> 00:18:18,319
[SPEAKER_02] Ja kažem tako i tako, kažem nazva ću ja Medvedev.

98
00:18:18,799 --> 00:18:21,119
[SPEAKER_02] On nazove Medvedev, pora to mi, kaže nazva ću on.

99
00:18:23,279 --> 00:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_02] Peto, prošlog mjesec dana mene preko odvjetnika kontaktira opet taj Krstoklarić, nije nitko zvao.

100
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:36,880
[SPEAKER_02] Ja kažem, maj dobro, probaću ja preko jednog hadezeovca čije poruke još.

101
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:38,000
